            <title>[LU-9603] Fix dependency for latest version bash in test-framework.sh</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9603</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the solution to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8576&quot; title=&quot;test-framework.sh is hard coded with o2ib0&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-8576&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-8576&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, h2nettype() has this line &lt;br/&gt;
if &#160;[[ -v NETTYPE ]], where -v is not a recognized option for bash versions &amp;lt; 4.2.&lt;br/&gt;
This needs to be fixed as bash version update should not be required for the scripts.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
